                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.01 Foreign Control/184: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Geneva (<persName corresp="#p_VSRG1" type="from"
                            >Gilbert</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-01-11T13:00:00+01:00"
                            >January 11, 1932—1 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received January 11—1 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>9. From <persName corresp="#p_RSJ1">Reber</persName>. Arrived this morning.
                    Committee meeting postponed until January 25th.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_VSRG1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Gilbert</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
